#: reproducible_environments/02/package-management.md:3
msgid "## Package management systems"
msgstr "## Sistemas de gestión de paquetes"

#: reproducible_environments/02/package-management.md:5
msgid ""
"Package managers install and keep track of the different software packages "
"(and their versions) that you use within an environment. There are quite a "
"few to choose from, for example Yum, Zypper, dpkg, and Nix (which will be "
"mentioned briefly later in the [Binder](#Binder_section) section). We're "
"going to focus on [Conda](https://conda.io/en/latest/), which has a number "
"of useful functionalities."
msgstr ""
"Los administradores de paquetes instalan y realizan un seguimiento de los "
"diferentes paquetes de software (y sus versiones) que utiliza en un entorno."
" Hay bastantes para elegir, por ejemplo, Yum, Zypper, dpkg y Nix (que se "
"mencionarán brevemente mas adelante en la sección [Binder] (# "
"Binder_section)). Nos centraremos en [Conda] (https://conda.io/en/latest/), "
"que tiene una serie de funcionalidades útiles."

#: reproducible_environments/02/package-management.md:7
msgid "<a name=\"What_does_Conda_do\"></a>"
msgstr "<a name=\"What_does_Conda_do\"></a>"

