"Conda allows users to create any number of environments which are entirely "
"separate, and to quickly and easily change between them."
msgstr ""
"Conda permite a los usuarios crear cualquier cantidad de entornos "
"completamente separados y cambiar rápida y fácilmente entre ellos."

