"```\n"
"number-value: 42\n"
"floating-point-value: 3.141592\n"
"boolean-value: true\n"
"\n"
"# strings can be both 'single-quoted` and \"double-quoted\"\n"
"string-value: 'Bonjour'\n"
"```"
